I feel him... this song is so sad. We need to listen to our youth of all colors, and be there for them when they need us most. What some of them go through every day is inexcusable and a tragedy... Until now I did not even consider being a child psychologist, but in the absence of adult leadership for our kids, maybe this could be the best way to help people and ensure a better tomorrow...

The trend of awesome hooks that have nothing to do with the song continues. lol Great track.
